sentences.english: Large-span suspended-dome was adopted in Ji nan Olympic Center Gymnasium.
sentences.chinese: 济南奥体中心体育馆采用大跨度弦支穹顶结构。

sentences.english: You can zoom in now and get a pretty nice view of the Dome.

sentences.english: We took the kids to Florence to see Brunelleschi's dome.
sentences.chinese: 我们带着孩子到佛罗伦萨看布鲁内莱斯基的穹顶。

sentences.english: The steel roof structure of a gymnasium is a kind of large span string-dome structure system.
sentences.chinese: 某体育馆钢屋盖为大跨度弦支穹顶结构。

sentences.english: Based on the huge dome and the crescent sign, I guess it must be an Islamic structure.

sentences.english: Phase two will see the completion of the central dome.
sentences.chinese: 第二阶段则将完成中央穹顶的建造。
穹顶则打开了全新的维度。

sentences.english: The large pavilions are double layered dome structures.
sentences.chinese: 大型竹亭是双层穹顶结构。

sentences.english: Four domed chambers surround the Taj.
sentences.chinese: 泰姬的四周围绕着四个小穹顶。

sentences.english: The beautiful dome of Mannheim church.
sentences.chinese: 漂亮的曼海姆教堂穹顶。

sentences.english: Schwedler single-layer latticed domes belongs to structure of imperfection sensitivity;
sentences.chinese: 施威德勒穹顶属于缺陷敏感性结构。

sentences.english: Now there were a number of problems with domes.
sentences.chinese: 然而穹顶建筑是有一些问题的。

sentences.english: The ultimate load-bearing capacity of a new dome formed by means of post-tensioning is studied in the paper.
sentences.chinese: 本文研究的是一种新型张拉穹顶结构的承载力性能。

sentences.english: We are all under the dome.
Suspend-dome structure is adopted in Pingshan Basketball Gymnasium for Universidad 2011 Shenzhen.
sentences.chinese: 深圳坪山体育馆屋顶采用新颖的弦支穹顶结构体系。

sentences.english: Genetic algorithm method is applied into the optimal prestress design of suspen-domes.
sentences.chinese: 采用遗传算法对弦支穹顶结构进行了预应力优化设计。
